{"tid":158710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英女王御准   英國將正式啟動脫歐","createTime":"2017-03-16T12:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T05:13:04.000Z","uid":62257,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9eb73bd3919640f96160344fcdb43f4c22a4e57","tid":158710,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rti.org.tw/news/detail/?recordId=332402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F%3FrecordId%3D332402&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=669c22a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rti.org.tw/news/detail/?recordId=332402</a><br />\n女王伊莉莎白二世(Elizabeth II)今天(16日)御准(Royal Assent)英國國會通過的脫離歐洲聯盟(EU)法案，賦予英國首相梅伊(Theresa May)權力，讓她可隨時啟動歐盟里斯本條約(Lisbon Treaty)第50條條文(Article 50)，展開為期兩年的脫歐協商。<br />\n<br />\n梅伊已經表示，她將於3月底之前去函歐洲理事會(European Council)，通知英國將啟動脫歐。<br />\n<br />\n英國國會下議院議長貝爾考(John Bercow)日前宣布國會通過脫歐法案後，執政的保守黨議員發出歡呼慶賀聲。<br />\n<br />\n梅伊表示，她準備在英國國會發表演說，告訴議員們將啟動里斯本條約第50條，接著去函歐洲理事會通知脫歐。等到梅伊去函通知後，歐盟執委會(European Commission)只要花48小時的時間，就可發出第一份協商草案。<br />\n<br />\n不過，在第一份協商草案出爐後的數週或數個月，等到英國與歐盟雙方都準備好之後，雙方才會正式展開全面協商。"},{"pid":"ceacdaa576c6e6193a69ab392809b843dd247d52","tid":158710,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:46:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1319608-20170316.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1319608-20170316.htm&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=7910e673\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1319608-20170316.htm&h=7e5ae6ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1319608-20170316.htm</a><br />\n英女王批准脫歐法案生效　文翠珊：月底啟動脫歐程序<br />\n2017-03-16 HKT 19:35<br />\n<br />\n英女王伊利沙伯二世批准脫歐法案正式生效，授權首相文翠珊可以在任何時候啓動《里斯本條約》第50條的脫歐條款。<br />\n<br />\n文翠珊表示，她將去信歐洲理事會，知會對方會在本月底啟動脫歐程序。<br />\n<br />\n英國在去年進行脫歐公投，有百分之51.9投票民眾支持脫歐。"},{"pid":"0495ca044f31ad09081145e09b194e3ef8793030","tid":158710,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6790782cea7c225d47f0b72f77c3f1e149bc59ee","tid":158710,"uid":4850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a7e1e8e123a5d1618500a2b60446d83dd201f5","tid":158710,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0f9531f46dc5a19d80f6af3f80722498f5e62df","tid":158710,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:38:01.000Z","msg":"呢D例牌程序冇得拒絕，有咩好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c69e480e2edf0ddc071c8541b6c64f5ce1e47b","tid":158710,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:14:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢D例牌程序冇得拒絕，有咩好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有無試過俾君主否決過？"},{"pid":"aa07a04af7b6fa858d857f18a0de1195d3ea448a","tid":158710,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:19:49.000Z","msg":"幾時到蘇格蘭脫英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb2a897e0810906fa8dcd82ef064256f0252a09","tid":158710,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:31:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢D例牌程序冇得拒絕，有咩好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有無試過俾君主否決過？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有....1708 年的 Scottish Militia Bill....<br />\n之後就無再使用過..."},{"pid":"86e367b567f3534c3e9abfbfe2d4b7eb230f8974","tid":158710,"uid":26037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:36:03.000Z","msg":"脱歐程序 正式啟動"},{"pid":"78d1243a3529f3f60e5039f10c71a0869f1ec6d2","tid":158710,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:44:15.000Z","msg":"乜撚梅伊"},{"pid":"271e0f9be57e3098323af35b6b46772da958c4f7","tid":158710,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:54:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢D例牌程序冇得拒絕，有咩好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有無試過俾君主否決過？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有....1708 年的 Scottish Militia Bill....<br />\n之後就無再使用過...</blockquote><br />\n邊似得鄰國成日搞虛權實化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373f72c74c817eed086e83f6ca07549bda36b2b9","tid":158710,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚梅伊</blockquote><br />\n台灣報導"}]}